        "TileImage": "$($repository 26bb164c-282d-4bce-b8a4-cbaa2da73432).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning, 47. We’ve learned that the head of the crime syndicate, &quot;SHAHIN ABDUL-BARR MAALOUF&quot; intends to acquire a massive diamond in Marrakesh, which he plans to use to make a satellite modified laser weapon  that could pose a global threat. Fortunately, his operatives must follow a courier for a considerable time after receiving the passcode in order to retrieve the diamond from one of three potential contacts. Kill all three possible couriers will thwart his plan.Good luck,47.",
